I tried using ChatGPT and Claude, but getting one good result was very different from getting consistently good results every day. I still had to find the angle, write the prompt, judge the output, repair it, and return tomorrow with another idea.&lt;p&gt;And thus, Feral was born - it's a content creation engine that generates text + image creative to promote your stuff, in a manner that's conducive for social media.&lt;p&gt;The entire harness around Feral's content creation pipeline consists of marketing, copywriting and psychology principles. It understands your business, but equally importantly, it understands what your customers tick; their dreams and desires, and then it creates content that speaks in their language.&lt;p&gt;You can try it here:&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://feralhq.com" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://feralhq.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;There is a 5-day free trial, then it is $45/month.&lt;p&gt;I would genuinely appreciate feedback!&lt;p&gt;reply&lt;/p&gt;
